Name: AA Touch Gun!
About the game: Classic timekiller. Defend yourself from the attack of the aircraft. Destroy all the planes. You can get bonuses for the destruction of enemies. Watch out for small and fast planes. Control is carried out with the mouse. Click on the aircraft. You need to hold out as long as possible and shoot down all the planes.
